|away from keyboard. When spectators go AFK, they can and should alter their ''/name'' accordingly. Going AFK on a nearly full server is considered disruptive and can result in a kick.
|-
|''auth''
|authentication, a key for registered players to identify. Often used as synonym for player accounts or [[privileges]].
|-
|''bb''
|[[bomber-ball]], a game mode.
